Description:
   Arcaneshield is the Brawler's signature remort shield. It encases the
   caster in a shimmering arcane barrier that absorbs magical damage. Similar
   in structure to iceshield, it is a purely defensive shield with no reactive
   damage, but provides very high absorption and durability.

   The key difference from iceshield is that arcaneshield ONLY absorbs
   non-physical (magical) damage. Physical attacks pass through the barrier
   entirely unaffected.

   Shield properties:
     - Type: ARCANE_SHIELD (can coexist with other shields)
     - Reactive Damage: None (purely absorptive)
     - Absorption: 50% + (pseudo_level / 6)% of magical damage absorbed
     - Hit Points: 15,000 + (pseudo_level * 50) -- shield breaks when depleted
     - Duration: pseudo_level / 15 rounds (halved on login)
     - Physical Bypass: Physical damage is NOT absorbed

   Arcaneshield can coexist with other shield effects.
*******************************************************************************
